title: Joey Logano Advances To Chase Eliminator Round With Dominant Charlotte Victory (Ford Motor Company)
text: ( Source : Ford Motor Company ) · Joey Logano 's win today is his fourth NASCAR Sprint Cup Series victory of the season and 12th of his career. · Logano advances to the Eliminator Round for the second consecutive year after winning his third
